The '''Accademia di Belle Arti di Palermo''' ("Academy of Fine Arts of Palermo") is a public tertiary academy of art in [[Palermo]], [[Sicily]]. It was established in 1780.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Giovanna Cassese|title=Accademie Patrimoni di Belle Arti|publisher=Gangemi Editore, 2013|isbn=88-492-2671-3}}</ref>

