'''Posthumanist art''' refers to [[art]] that can only be created in some part through the aid of [[digital technology]]. [[posthumanism|Posthumanist]] art can be either human-conceived, or machine-produced in whole or in part. The extent to which the human element is involved in the creation, whether by direct manipulation of the [[technology]], or by creation of the [[algorithm]] through which the art is created, can vary.

